{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"b829f8956cb30987ca7cc4","title":"BK7252N 固件编译说明","desc":"","updated":1780371367065,"created":1780371330030,"custom":{},"fname":"芯片SDK相关.BK7252N-编译说明","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"921a2310c5bea5fcb58750df7e383075","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"芯片SDK相关.BK7252N-编译说明","id":"b829f8956cb30987ca7cc4","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.bk7252n-烧录教程","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":117,"offset":137},"end":{"line":4,"column":138,"offset":158},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.bk7252n-烧录教程"}}],"anchors":{"bk7252n-固件编译说明":{"type":"header","text":"BK7252N 固件编译说明","value":"bk7252n-固件编译说明","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"1-环境准备":{"type":"header","text":"1. 环境准备","value":"1-环境准备","line":14,"column":0,"depth":2},"11-必备软件":{"type":"header","text":"1.1 必备软件","value":"11-必备软件","line":16,"column":0,"depth":3},"12-工具链路径":{"type":"header","text":"1.2 工具链路径","value":"12-工具链路径","line":24,"column":0,"depth":3},"13-工作目录":{"type":"header","text":"1.3 工作目录","value":"13-工作目录","line":36,"column":0,"depth":3},"2-核心编译命令bk7252n":{"type":"header","text":"2. 核心编译命令（BK7252N）","value":"2-核心编译命令bk7252n","line":46,"column":0,"depth":2},"3-编译过程从头到尾":{"type":"header","text":"3. 编译过程（从头到尾）","value":"3-编译过程从头到尾","line":67,"column":0,"depth":2},"31-解析---beken-并生成平台配置":{"type":"header","text":"3.1 解析 --beken 并生成平台配置","value":"31-解析---beken-并生成平台配置","line":71,"column":0,"depth":3},"32-scons-编译与链接":{"type":"header","text":"3.2 SCons 编译与链接","value":"32-scons-编译与链接","line":90,"column":0,"depth":3},"33-打包与输出目录post_actionpy":{"type":"header","text":"3.3 打包与输出目录（post_action.py）","value":"33-打包与输出目录post_actionpy","line":97,"column":0,"depth":3},"4-常用辅助命令":{"type":"header","text":"4. 常用辅助命令","value":"4-常用辅助命令","line":109,"column":0,"depth":2},"5-与配置产物相关的路径速查":{"type":"header","text":"5. 与配置、产物相关的路径速查","value":"5-与配置产物相关的路径速查","line":123,"column":0,"depth":2},"6-文档信息":{"type":"header","text":"6. 文档信息","value":"6-文档信息","line":136,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"z5f47zwafnfmykvy3tz21fi","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bk7252n-固件编译说明\">BK7252N 固件编译说明<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bk7252n-固件编译说明\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"bk7252n-固件编译说明-1\">BK7252N 固件编译说明<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bk7252n-固件编译说明-1\"></a></h1>\n<p>本文档说明本仓库（<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code>，RT-Thread + Beken BK7252N）在 Linux 下的<strong>编译命令</strong>与<strong>从配置到产物</strong>的完整流程。烧录步骤见同仓库 <a href=\"/notes/40a0c1d0224426bb0700ea\">BK7252N 烧录教程（基于当前工程产物）</a>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"1-环境准备\">1. 环境准备<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#1-环境准备\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"11-必备软件\">1.1 必备软件<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#11-必备软件\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>项目</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>SCons</strong></td><td>工程使用 SCons 作为构建系统</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Python</strong></td><td>SCons 与 <code>tools/scripts/post_action.py</code> 依赖 Python</td></tr><tr><td><strong>ARM GCC 工具链</strong></td><td><code>arm-none-eabi-gcc</code> 等，<strong>版本需与 <code>rtconfig.py</code> 中 <code>SDK_TOOLCHAIN</code>（当前为 <code>5.4.1</code>）一致</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h3 id=\"12-工具链路径\">1.2 工具链路径<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#12-工具链路径\"></a></h3>\n<p>根目录 <a href=\"/../../rtconfig.py\"><code>rtconfig.py</code></a> 默认将 <code>EXEC_PATH</code> 设为：</p>\n<p><code>/opt/gcc-arm-none-eabi-5_4-2016q3/bin</code></p>\n<p>若工具链安装在其他目录，请设置环境变量 <strong><code>RTT_EXEC_PATH</code></strong> 指向该 <code>bin</code> 目录（末尾带不带 <code>/</code> 一般均可，以本机实测为准）。</p>\n<p>可选：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><code>RTT_ROOT</code></strong>：若 RT-Thread 不在工程默认相对路径 <code>rt-thread</code>，可通过此变量指定。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"13-工作目录\">1.3 工作目录<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#13-工作目录\"></a></h3>\n<p>所有编译命令均在<strong>工程根目录</strong>（包含 <code>SConstruct</code>、<code>rtconfig.py</code> 的目录）下执行：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> /path/to/bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"2-核心编译命令bk7252n\">2. 核心编译命令（BK7252N）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#2-核心编译命令bk7252n\"></a></h2>\n<p>日常全量编译固件（并行数按 CPU 调整）：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">scons --beken<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>bk7252n -j8\n</code></pre>\n<p>等价变体示例：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">scons --beken<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>bk7252n -j4\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>说明：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>--beken=bk7252n</code> 必选，用于选择 BK7252N 平台并触发对应的配置与链接脚本（见下文流程）。</li>\n<li><code>-jN</code> 为 SCons 并行任务数，可按机器核数修改。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"3-编译过程从头到尾\">3. 编译过程（从头到尾）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#3-编译过程从头到尾\"></a></h2>\n<p>整体可概括为：<strong>按芯片切换 BSP 配置 → SCons 编译链接生成 ELF/_bin → 打包工具生成烧录镜像并整理到 <code>out/</code></strong>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"31-解析---beken-并生成平台配置\">3.1 解析 <code>--beken</code> 并生成平台配置<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#31-解析---beken-并生成平台配置\"></a></h3>\n<p>SCons 读取 <a href=\"/../../rt-thread/tools/building.py\"><code>rt-thread/tools/building.py</code></a> 时，在常规固件编译路径下会执行：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>调用 <code>generate_sys_config</code></strong>（Linux 为 <a href=\"/../../tools/scripts/generate_sys_config.sh\"><code>tools/scripts/generate_sys_config.sh</code></a>）<br>\n对 <code>bk7252n</code> 会：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>将 <code>beken378/app/config/sys_config_bk7252n.h</code> 同步为根目录 <code>config/sys_config.h</code>（内容变化时更新）；</li>\n<li>将 <code>config/rtconfig/rtconfig_bk7252n.h</code> 同步为根目录 <code>rtconfig.h</code>；</li>\n<li>用预处理器展开 <code>config/bk7252n_boot.lds</code> 生成工程根目录下的 <strong><code>link.lds</code></strong>（实际链接脚本）；</li>\n<li>写入 <strong><code>.platform</code></strong> 文件，内容为 <code>bk7252n</code>，标记当前目标芯片。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>读取 Flash 容量</strong><br>\n从 <code>config/sys_config.h</code> 中解析 <code>CFG_FLASH_SELECTION_TYPE</code> 及其对应数值（例如 4M 对应 <code>0x400000</code>），用于后续打包选择分区 JSON 模板。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>追加 POST_ACTION</strong><br>\n在链接完成、<code>objcopy</code> 生成 <code>rtthread.bin</code> 之后，追加执行：</p>\n<p><code>python tools/scripts/post_action.py bk7252n &#x3C;flash_size></code></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"32-scons-编译与链接\">3.2 SCons 编译与链接<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#32-scons-编译与链接\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>根 <a href=\"/../../SConstruct\"><code>SConstruct</code></a> 使用 RT-Thread 的 <code>PrepareBuilding</code> / <code>DoBuilding</code> 收集各子目录 <code>SConscript</code>，编译得到目标 <strong><code>rtthread.elf</code></strong>。</li>\n<li><a href=\"/../../rtconfig.py\"><code>rtconfig.py</code></a> 中 <code>POST_ACTION</code>（在 Beken 逻辑追加 pack 之前）包含：将 <code>rtthread.elf</code> 转为 <strong><code>rtthread.bin</code></strong>，并执行 <code>size</code> 等。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>BK7252N 闭源/预编译库（如 <code>libip_7252n_*</code>、<code>libble_7252n_*</code> 等）由 Beken 侧 <code>SConscript</code> 按芯片型号选择，编译日志中会出现 <code>using ... libxxx_7252n.a</code> 一类提示。</p>\n<h3 id=\"33-打包与输出目录post_actionpy\">3.3 打包与输出目录（<code>post_action.py</code>）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#33-打包与输出目录post_actionpy\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/../../tools/scripts/post_action.py\"><code>tools/scripts/post_action.py</code></a> 根据 <strong>芯片名</strong> 与 <strong>Flash 大小</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>生成 <strong><code>config.json</code></strong>：bootloader 使用 <code>tools/beken_packager/bootloader_bk7252n_uart1_v1.0.14.bin</code>，app 段指向 <code>rtthread.bin</code>；</li>\n<li>调用 <strong><code>tools/beken_packager/beken_packager</code></strong>（Linux 下为 <code>./tools/beken_packager/beken_packager</code>）生成完整升级包与 UART 包等；</li>\n<li>清空并重建 <strong><code>out/</code></strong>，将 <code>rtthread.bin</code>、<code>rtthread.elf</code>、<code>rtthread.map</code>、合成镜像、bootloader 副本等移入其中。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>当前 <code>sys_config_bk7252n.h</code> 中典型配置为 <strong>4M Flash</strong>（<code>CFG_FLASH_SELECTION_TYPE</code> → <code>FLASH_SELECTION_TYPE_4M</code>），产物命名中会带有 <strong><code>4M</code></strong> 版本字段（具体文件名以构建输出为准，常见形式包括 <code>all_4M.*.bin</code>、<code>rtthread_uart_4M.*.bin</code> 等）。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"4-常用辅助命令\">4. 常用辅助命令<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#4-常用辅助命令\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>用途</th><th>命令</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>清理构建</td><td><code>scons -c</code> 或 <code>scons --clean</code>（习惯上与 <code>--beken=bk7252n</code> 同用）</td></tr><tr><td>图形/菜单配置（RT-Thread BSP）</td><td><code>scons --beken=bk7252n --menuconfig</code></td></tr><tr><td>仅重建/清理某类 Beken 静态库（较少用）</td><td><code>scons --beken=bk7252n --buildlib=&#x3C;name></code> / <code>--cleanlib=&#x3C;name></code></td></tr><tr><td>批量构建该平台全部库</td><td><code>scons --beken=bk7252n --buildlibs</code></td></tr><tr><td>查看 SCons 与本工程选项</td><td><code>scons --beken=bk7252n --help</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p><strong>注意：</strong> <code>--buildlibs</code> / <code>--cleanlibs</code> 会在脚本内多次调用 <code>scons --buildlib=...</code>，首次完整 SDK 搭建或切换大版本时可参考；日常改应用代码一般只需 <strong><code>scons --beken=bk7252n -jN</code></strong>。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"5-与配置产物相关的路径速查\">5. 与配置、产物相关的路径速查<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#5-与配置产物相关的路径速查\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>内容</th><th>路径</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>BK7252N 芯片系统配置（源）</td><td><code>beken378/app/config/sys_config_bk7252n.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>编译时使用的副本</td><td><code>config/sys_config.h</code>（由脚本从上面复制）</td></tr><tr><td>RT-Thread 配置头（源）</td><td><code>config/rtconfig/rtconfig_bk7252n.h</code> → 根目录 <code>rtconfig.h</code></td></tr><tr><td>链接脚本源</td><td><code>config/bk7252n_boot.lds</code> → 预处理后 <code>link.lds</code></td></tr><tr><td>最终固件与 map 等</td><td><code>out/</code></td></tr><tr><td>打包工具与 Bootloader 二进制</td><td><code>tools/beken_packager/</code></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"6-文档信息\">6. 文档信息<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#6-文档信息\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>适用工程</strong>：<code>bk7252n_sdk-SDK_3.0.76.1_witch_lcd</code></li>\n<li><strong>整理日期</strong>：2026-05-09</li>\n<li><strong>流程依据</strong>：<code>rt-thread/tools/building.py</code>、<code>tools/scripts/generate_sys_config.sh</code>、<code>tools/scripts/post_action.py</code>、根目录 <code>SConstruct</code> / <code>rtconfig.py</code></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI 打印机固件文档库","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"8a8345555f63e0c00780aff37583c213","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":83},"end":{"line":8,"column":20,"offset":100},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目交接资料","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":115},"end":{"line":9,"column":18,"offset":130},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目交接资料"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"阶段性开发总结","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":145},"end":{"line":10,"column":14,"offset":156},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"阶段性开发总结"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"tutorial","position":{"start